        <p> {{ page.overview.intro|raw }} Tomorrow it is time again to change the accommodation, because unfortunately I could no longer book this apartment. At least I thought. </p>
        <p> As I finished myself, I got a message from the owner of the apartment that his staff is in the building today and that it takes care of the other apartments and whether I still needed anything. I thanked him and immediately informed him that I plan to leave the apartment around 11 a.m. so that he can let his cleaning team let me know. After a few seconds he wrote back and asked what was wrong, I would have booked until Saturday. After some back and forth, it turned out that we had spoken a little by each other. He said I can book the nights 10 - 16. So departure only on Saturday, March 17th. I had understood I can only until 16.03. remain. </p>
        <p> Now I have already booked accommodation from Friday to Sunday. This is not very expensive on the edge of the stand and happiness, because every change results in the costs of the first overnight stay. Well then I have 2 accommodations for the night from Friday to Saturday. </p>
