        <p> So I postponed this by packing to tonight or tomorrow and preferred to work on the blog. So I started looking for a baker to get a dry bun against hunger and then sit down in a cafe with a milkshake somewhere. </p>
        <p> I found a nice small shop in a side street and the display said, calories high 15. cookies, popcorn, cream cakes. Luckily I have control and ordered only one pineapple fruit shake without extra sugar. Some time later, the lunch hungry reported and the cafe filled up. Then I made my way to a restaurant with a beach view. I stayed there for some time and enjoyed the view before I made my way back to the apartment, because the work was slowly called again. </p>
